<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); font-size: 24px;">长津湖战役是抗美援朝第二次战役中东线战场在长津湖地区遂行的一次反击作战。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); font-size: 24px;">长津湖战役中，中国人民志愿军第9兵团3个军，在气温零下20多摄氏度、冻伤较多、兵力不足的条件下，与武器装备世界一流、战功显赫的美军第10军，于1950年11月27日至12月24日在朝鲜长津湖地区进行了直接较量，创造了抗美援朝战争中全歼美军一个整团的纪录，迫使美军王牌部队经历了有史以来“路程最长的退却”。这次战役，收复了三八线以北的东部广大地区。志愿军在东西两线同时大捷，一举扭转了战场态势，成为朝鲜战争的拐点，为最终到来的停战谈判奠定了胜利基础。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705115345219073176.jpg" title="1705115345219073176.jpg" alt="dc1c2d0f656cf54f629d7250154052f6.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">什么是英雄？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">彤云郁郁。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">雪域森森,长津阔远凛冽。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">帝国挑唆烽火，为和平决。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">凌云壮志不改,怎惧他、敌顽凶劣？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">战勇猛，对骄狂、肉搏染江流血。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">大炮声声天裂。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">无制空，冲锋被封悲切。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">阻断交通，给养困难不接。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">忠心赤诚报国，任冰雕、荡气铁骨。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">看大地，赤帜展、<span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">风卷猎猎！</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); font-size: 24px;">认识英雄，更应铭记英雄，因为“英雄是民族最闪亮的坐标，是时代最坚实的脊梁，是历史最鲜亮的底色，是奉献最崇高的礼赞，是身边最朴实的奋斗。”</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); font-size: 24px;">在抗美援朝中，英雄连队——七连与他们的战友们坚守阵地，让敌人无法进攻和撤退。他们在冰雪中战胜了疲惫和饥饿。他们用毅力歌唱了祖国的大好河山，用鲜血染红了迎风飘扬的五星红旗。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(87, 72, 75); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 251, 247); font-size: 24px;">他们走着坚定的步伐，把烟雾缭绕的中国变成了蓝天白云和小康生活，而我们怎能心安理得享受先辈用鲜血为我们打造的和平盛世，作为新时代青年，应志存高远、忠于祖国，努力做新时代具有远大理想和坚定信念的爱国者。“志不立，天下无可成之事”。一个人的理想只有同国家的前途和民族的命运相结合才有价值，一个人的追求只有同社会的需要和人民的利益相一致才有意义。</span></p>